    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "At 10:00 a.m. today, SAC Willis, Houston, called in and stated",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "that [REDACTED] a business man in Houston, Texas, had furnished",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "certain pictures taken by a friend of his, [REDACTED] of the [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Houston, Texas, and had related that [REDACTED] had been flying",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "with a friend in a private plane from California to Houston and that at a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "point about 30 miles east of Lone Pine, California, some object lying on the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "ground made a very strong reflection and they made a check to determine what",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "would cause this bright reflection. They finally landed the plane and found",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "an object which could be described as being 8' in diameter with wings about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "4' long. The object is about 1' in thickness and in the center there appears",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "to be some type of gyroscope. The wings apparently are fitted with some type",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "of jet propulsion. An examination was made by [REDACTED] and his friend and they",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "could find no identifying marks and took photographs of the object they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "observed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "SAC Willis stated he had informed Lieutenant [REDACTED] of the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "AAF, Ellington Field, and [REDACTED] the Army representative in Houston,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "of this object and that [REDACTED] would be interviewed that morning in the Houston",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Office with Lieutenant [REDACTED] being present. Lieutenant [REDACTED] wanted the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "statements of [REDACTED] taken down by a stenographer and he will furnish the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "stenographer for that purpose.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "I instructed SAC Willis to furnish complete details of this matter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "by air mail special delivery, including a copy of the photograph. I further",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "instructed that he furnish the same details to the proper field office because",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "unquestionably the Bureau would want to run this thing out.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "After talking with you, I phoned SAC Willis back and told him to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "insure the presence of a Bureau Agent at the time this object was examined by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "the Army Air Forces and that he should make proper arrangements with the office",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "in California to see that an Agent was present. I also told him to advise me",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "of the developments.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "status": "blank"
    },
